81
00:05:05,597 --> 00:05:07,097
200 mortals matched.

82
00:05:07,574 --> 00:05:10,059
100 happily ever afters
before I'm allowed back.

83
00:05:10,498 --> 00:05:11,810
- Back where?
- Olympus.

84
