this... magic.

97
00:05:47,268 --> 00:05:49,306
Do you see a bow?

98
00:05:52,021 --> 00:05:55,270
How long do you think this quest
will take you... bowless?

99
00:05:55,605 --> 00:05:57,982
- Two weeks, max.
- Two weeks?

100
00:05:58,151 --> 00:05:59,775
- Make it ten days.
- Final answer?

101
