A couple of nights a week,
I mediate a group.

163
00:08:53,907 --> 00:08:56,535
- Look at that. You got a card.
- Yeah. I've got a card.

164
00:08:56,704 --> 00:08:59,648
It's a singles group.
Kind of an informal, roundtable thing.

165
00:08:59,773 --> 00:09:02,671
We discuss relationships
and healthy dating patterns.

166
00:09:02,977 --> 00:09:05,002
