168
00:09:09,274 --> 00:09:12,426
- What are you saying, Trevor?
- I'm saying I've got a job to do...

169
00:09:13,286 --> 00:09:15,073
Find Holly,
match another 99 couples.

170
00:09:15,198 --> 00:09:16,731
I got a lot to do before I get home.

171
00:09:16,856 --> 00:09:18,855
I wasn't gonna get it done
in that place.

172
00:09:19,337 --> 00:09:20,434
You were faking.

173
00:09:22,395 --> 00:09:25,105
Look, Trevor, I just staked
my professional reputation on you.

174
00:09:25,274 --> 00:09:26,890
Which was sweet. Keep it.

175
00:09:27,015 --> 00:09:29,193
- You want one? On me.
- What? No.

176
00:09:29,636 --> 00:09:32,863
Look, Trevor. You are not a god.
You are a man.

177
00:09:33,032 --> 00:09:35,240
I'll see you tonight.
Sounds like these people need me.

178
