and I promise you'll be packed tonight.

201
00:11:34,486 --> 00:11:36,787
Margaret, I respect your decision.

202
00:11:36,912 --> 00:11:39,707
I do. All I'm suggesting is
that if you're going to continue

203
00:11:39,832 --> 00:11:41,852
to place an ad in the personals,
it might be wise

204
00:11:41,977 --> 00:11:44,786
to mention your chastity pledge
within the text.

205
00:11:47,207 --> 00:11:50,145
It looks like we've got time
for one more person.

206
00:11:53,252 --> 00:11:55,333
Trevor,
maybe it'll be a good idea

207
00:11:55,458 --> 00:11:57,646
